=1403-1412&amp;doi=10.1056%2FNEJMoa070543&amp;pmid=17914041">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Pooler BD, Baumel MJ, Cash BD, et al. Screening CT colonography: multicenter survey of patient experience, preference, and potential impact on adherence. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2012;198(6): 1361–1366.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.11.7671">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22623549/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Screening+CT+colonography%3A+multicenter+survey+of+patient+experience%2C+preference%2C+and+potential+impact+on+adherence&amp;author=BD+Pooler&amp;author=MJ+Baumel&amp;author=BD+Cash&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1361-1366&amp;doi=10.2214%2FAJR.11.7671&amp;pmid=22623549">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</div><div id="r11" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Knudsen AB, Lansdorp-Vogelaar I, Rutter CM, et al. Cost-effectiveness of computed tomographic colonography screening for colorectal cancer in the Medicare population. <em>J Natl Cancer Inst</em> 2010;102(16):1238–1252.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/jnci/djq242">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20664028/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cost-effectiveness+of+computed+tomographic+colonography+screening+for+colorectal+cancer+in+the+Medicare+population&amp;author=AB+Knudsen&amp;author=I+Lansdorp