261-010-9625-5&amp;pmid=20473667">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">14.</div><div id="r14" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Fidler JL, Fletcher JG, Johnson CD, et al. Understanding interpretive errors in radiologists learning computed tomography colonography. <em>Acad Radiol</em> 2004;11(7):750–756.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.acra.2004.03.052">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15217592/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Understanding+interpretive+errors+in+radiologists+learning+computed+tomography+colonography&amp;author=JL+Fidler&amp;author=JG+Fletcher&amp;author=CD+Johnson&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=Acad+Radiol&amp;pages=750-756&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.acra.2004.03.052&amp;pmid=15217592">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="r15" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Krupinski EA. What can the radiologist teach CAD: lessons from CT colonoscopy. <em>Acad Radiol</em> 2009;16(1):1–3.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.acra.2008.10.004">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19064205/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=What+can+the+radiologist+teach+CAD%3A+lessons+from+CT+colonoscopy&amp;author=EA+Krupinski&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=Acad+Radiol&amp;pages=1-3&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.acra.2008.10.004&amp;pmid=19064205">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">16.</div><div id